headline: T. ROWE PRICE GROUP, INC., DECLARES QUARTERLY DIVIDEND AND ANNOUNCES ANNUAL MEETING VOTING RESULTS
summary: T. Rowe Price Group, Inc. (NASDAQ-GS: TROW), announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly dividend of $1.27 per share payable June 27, 2025, to stockholders of record as of the close of business on June 13, 2025.
